Mail Monster - Source Code
==========================

A simple utility for splitting mbox files by month.

Build Instructions
------------------

To build all project artifacts and install them in your local Maven repository:

    mvn clean install

Usage
-----

To read a single mbox file and sort it into mbox files by month:

    java -jar mailmonster-VERSION-jar-with-dependencies.jar MBOX_FILE OUTPUT_DIR

To read a directory of mbox files and sort them into mbox files by month:

    java -jar mailmonster-VERSION-jar-with-dependencies.jar MBOX_DIR OUTPUT_DIR
